title: Thom Hartmann Program - October 17 2013
description:
October 17, 2013
The Thom Hartmann Program 

Hour One: How the "know nothing" press extended the shutdown / Plus, Everything You Know is Wrong...about the # 12?  William Gladstone, The Power of Twelve

Hour Two: What madness lurks in the Tea Party brain?  Mike Papantonio, Ring of Fire Radio / Plus, the debt deal winners & sore losers... Professor Peter Morici, Newsmax

Hour Three: Geeky Science - where would we be without plants?
